article.description: — Josh Corbin had 20 points in Robert Morris’ 71-66 win against Central Michigan on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Corbin has 20, Robert Morris beats Central Michigan 71-66
article.linkText: Corbin has 20, Robert Morris beats Central Michigan 71-66
article.story: MOUNT PLEASANT, Mich. -- — Josh Corbin had 20 points in Robert Morris’ 71-66 win against Central Michigan on Wednesday night. Corbin shot 7 for 13, including 6 for 11 from beyond the arc for the Colonials (4-6). Kahliel Spear added 18 points while going 7 of 14 and 4 of 5 from the free throw line, and he also had 15 rebounds and seven assists. Enoch Cheeks recorded 17 points and shot 6 for 13 (1 for 3 from 3-point range) and 4 of 6 from the free throw line. Jesse Zarzuela led the way for the Chippewas (4-5) with 25 points. Markus Harding added 13 points, seven rebounds and two blocks for Central Michigan. Reggie Bass also had 10 points, eight rebounds and two steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
